
Overview of noun hacker

The noun hacker has 4 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                         
1. (1) hacker -- (someone who plays golf poorly)
2. hacker, cyber-terrorist, cyberpunk -- (a programmer who breaks into computer systems in order to steal or change or destroy information as a form of cyber-terrorism)
3. hacker -- (a programmer for whom computing is its own reward; may enjoy the challenge of breaking into other computers but does no harm; "true hackers subscribe to a code of ethics and look down upon crackers")
4. hack, drudge, hacker -- (one who works hard at boring tasks)
